column2: 4th Floor, Food Court, Bangalore Central Mall, 9th Block, Jayanagar, Bangalore
column15: 'RATED\\n  This place is situated at the food court at JP nagar Central. I went here to grab some quick dinner and ordered their chicken biryani combo priced at Rs. 299 inclusive of taxes. The combo meal looked colourful and attractive but failed to live upto the expectations the guy at the counter had built while advertising the food. The biryani was okayish not great. It had good no.of chicken pieces in it. The raita that was served to me was plain yogurt with some salt in it. For some reason they serve chilli vinegar with biryani. The pepper chicken that was served along was actually good. The portions are quite huge. I would not recommend this place until and unless you are at JP nagar central and do not want to eat at any of the other food joints at their food court. Definitely not going back there ??')
